=head1 NAME

Lua-cxx Gtk support

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    require "luacxx.Gtk";

    -- Get these namespaces
    local cairo = require "cairo";
    local Gtk = require "Gtk";

    - Examine Gtk's exported objects. There are over 1,000!
    print(Gtk);

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This subdirectory provides support for GObject introspection. While much of the
groundwork has been laid down, not all Gtk object types are supported (like
enums, constants, and more advanced object construction).
